====United Kingdom====
  +
{{Main|2011 United Kingdom protests}}
  +
The '''2011 United Kingdom protests''' are ongoing protests and riots in the [[United Kingdom]], starting in March 2011, [[Anti-austerity protests|fighting against austerity measures]] by the new coalition government.
  +   +
The protests escalated through March, and on 26 March 2011 protests coordinated by the [[Trades Union Congress]] with crowds approaching 500,000 people (in some estimates) took to [[London]]'s streets.<ref name=live>{{citenews|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/8407260/TUC-protest-march-live.html|title=TUC protest march: live|date=26 March 2011|accessdate=26 March 2011|publisher=''[[The Daily Telegraph]]''}}</ref>
